Everyone thought I was doomed,

102
00:05:28,020 --> 00:05:29,020
including myself.

103
00:05:31,180 --> 00:05:32,900
Then Dr. Gu helped you?

104
00:05:35,900 --> 00:05:37,900
You know why I keep calling him Boss?

105
00:05:40,460 --> 00:05:41,820
He's only two levels higher than me.

106
00:05:43,940 --> 00:05:45,780
But he's the opposite of me.

107
00:05:47,060 --> 00:05:49,180
He was famous after his first operation.

108
00:05:49,780 --> 00:05:52,300
He performed a thalamic tumor operation
at a very young age

109
00:05:53,660 --> 00:05:55,660
and became a legend
of Huaren's Neurosurgery Department.

110
00:05:56,660 --> 00:05:58,260
But I didn't expect

111
00:05:58,940 --> 00:06:00,660
that he would say

112
00:06:00,660 --> 00:06:01,900
to a loser who was forsaken by all

113
00:06:03,300 --> 00:06:05,780
and about to change profession,

114
00:06:09,380 --> 00:06:10,380
"If you don't mind,

115
00:06:12,660 --> 00:06:13,900
I need a first assistant".

116
00:06:24,660 --> 00:06:25,580
Fang Mingfan?

117
00:06:29,020 --> 00:06:29,580
Why are you back?

118
00:06:31,300 --> 00:06:31,780
What?

119
00:06:32,420 --> 00:06:34,500
I said since you've decided to give up,

120
00:06:34,500 --> 00:06:35,780
why do you still come to the hospital?

121
00:06:37,060 --> 00:06:38,060
A habit, I guess.

122
00:06:40,780 --> 00:06:41,940
Could be an instinct, too.

123
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,440
Fang Mingfan.

124
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:40,720
How much do you know
about the transsphenoidal approach

125
00:07:40,840 --> 00:07:41,640
of pituitary tumors?

126
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:44,120
I studied some videos

127
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,640
and watched some doctors do it.

128
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:48,880
Sorry for this.

129
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,360
But I need a first assistant.

130
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:56,600
I can be it.

131
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:01,120
Later, Boss came here for aid.

132
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:03,200
I didn't want to stay in China,

133
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:04,720
where people commented about me.

134
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,640
Then I followed him.

135
00:08:09,320 --> 00:08:10,280
So, Dr. Gu

136
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:12,320
became your boss instead of your senior.

137
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:16,200
Then why did he favor you that much?

138
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:18,640
I asked him why he picked me.

139
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,560
He didn't favor me.

140
00:08:21,440 --> 00:08:24,040
He said he just
didn't want to see a deserter.

141
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:26,360
He hated deserters.

142
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:30,360
And then?

143
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:32,120
When did you have

144
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,150
your second surgery?

145
00:08:41,640 --> 00:08:42,840
I'm not ready yet.

146
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:50,120
I know I'm useless.

147
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:51,640
Don't say that.

148
00:08:53,280 --> 00:08:55,120
You can't be as useless as me, anyway.

149
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:58,560
If you're not ready,

150
00:08:58,560 --> 00:08:59,840
take your time to get ready.

151
00:09:00,880 --> 00:09:03,320
Life is long.
There's always a second chance.

152
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:10,360
Yes, there is.

153
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:14,360
The free clinic is right ahead, I think.

154
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:16,360
Let's stay here and wait for them.

155
00:09:16,520 --> 00:09:17,600
Keep looking when it's light.

156
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,040
Come on.

157
00:09:25,880 --> 00:09:26,320
Be careful.

158
00:09:32,040 --> 00:09:32,640
Are you OK?

159
00:09:33,640 --> 00:09:34,360
I'm OK.

160
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,120
Gu Yunzheng.

161
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:55,840
Gu Yunzheng.

162
00:09:56,880 --> 00:09:57,680
Gu Yunzheng, wake up.

163
00:10:01,680 --> 00:10:02,680
You can't fall asleep.

164
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,120
Don't worry.

165
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,600
I didn't go into shock.

166
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:09,040
I'm just too sleepy.

167
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:11,560
I served the medical mission all day

168
00:10:12,400 --> 00:10:13,680
and walked such a long way.

169
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:15,320
I'm really exhausted.

170
00:10:18,680 --> 00:10:19,880
If you feel uncomfortable,

171
00:10:20,560 --> 00:10:21,400
you have to tell me.

172
00:10:23,920 --> 00:10:24,640
Su Wei'an,

173
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:26,840
to be honest,

174
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:30,840
I quite enjoy
being taken care of by you.

175
00:10:31,640 --> 00:10:32,640
So,

176
00:10:33,800 --> 00:10:35,600
if I feel uncomfortable,

177
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:37,280
I won't keep it from you.

178
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:41,040
Take some rest.

179
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:46,960
We can't walk like this.

180
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:48,200
I'll go get helpers.

181
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:48,920
You wait here for me.

182
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:57,360
Be careful, Su Wei'an!

183
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:00,640
Hurry up.

184
00:11:06,160 --> 00:11:06,640
Let's go.

185
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:26,720
There.

186
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:31,040
Gu Yunzheng.

187
00:11:32,040 --> 00:11:32,760
Gu Yunzheng.

188
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:34,000
Gu Yunzheng.

189
00:11:35,160 --> 00:11:35,760
Wake up.

190
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:37,680
Gu Yunzheng.

191
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,440
You freaked me out.

192
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:48,240
You're so strong.

193
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:50,120
Are you OK?

194
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:56,040
I really didn't want to wake up.

195
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:59,160
If you woke me up two seconds later,

196
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:01,720
I could kiss you.

197
00:12:03,040 --> 00:12:04,400
Look at this occasion.

198
00:12:05,800 --> 00:12:07,440
Don't involve me in this kind of dream.

199
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:11,400
What?

200
00:12:12,760 --> 00:12:14,000
Whatever you want to interfere with,

201
00:12:14,640 --> 00:12:16,040
you can't interfere with my dream.

202
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:22,720
Wei'an!

203
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:24,840
Hurry.

204
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:25,800
Get him in.

205
00:12:25,800 --> 00:12:26,760
Boss, what happened?

206
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:28,760
What happened?

207
00:12:28,760 --> 00:12:29,280
What's wrong?

208
00:12:29,540 --> 00:12:32,660
[Friendship Hospital]

209
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:45,960
You're awake.

210
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:47,880
How do you feel now?

211
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:49,720
I'm thirsty.

212
00:12:57,640 --> 00:12:58,160
Have some water.

213
00:12:58,680 --> 00:13:00,040
It stimulates the body's metabolism.

214
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:09,760
Hungry.

215
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:12,240
Here's some porridge. Want some?

216
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:20,320
I can't get up.

217
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:22,160
Forget it, then.

218
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:23,280
Let me feed you.

219
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:27,720
Here.

220
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:28,720
Get me up.

221
00:13:36,840 --> 00:13:38,160
Am I seeing this right?

222
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:41,640
Wei'an is feeding Dr. Gu.

223
00:13:47,560 --> 00:13:48,400
That night,

224
00:13:48,400 --> 00:13:50,480
what did they do in Labe Village?

225
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:54,240
Wei'an is like a different person now.

226
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:55,240
So is Dr. Gu.

227
00:13:57,040 --> 00:13:58,240
Did they eat some fruits

228
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:00,760
in the village

229
00:14:01,520 --> 00:14:02,480
and get poisoned?

230
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:45,760
Morning, Lan.

231
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:47,840
What are you calling me for?

232
00:14:48,240 --> 00:14:50,000
I'll be late for the square dance.

233
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:51,400
Square dance?

234
00:14:52,520 --> 00:14:54,120
But it's eight in the morning

235
00:14:54,120 --> 00:14:55,000
Beijing time, isn't it?

236
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:57,440
Even wage slaves don't work until nine.

237
00:14:58,640 --> 00:15:00,200
Fine. I'll talk for a few minutes.

238
00:15:01,480 --> 00:15:02,480
Wait.

239
00:15:03,280 --> 00:15:04,560
It's the weekend.

240
00:15:04,560 --> 00:15:06,800
Why do you still stay in the hospital,

241
00:15:06,920 --> 00:15:08,400
taking classes, doing experiments,

242
00:15:08,480 --> 00:15:09,960
or reading in the library?

243
00:15:10,920 --> 00:15:12,400
You waste your time in France.

244
00:15:13,400 --> 00:15:15,720
You don't enjoy your life at all.

245
00:15:16,040 --> 00:15:17,680
Who told you
I only stayed in the hospital?

246
00:15:18,440 --> 00:15:20,920
Last week, I volunteered
for a medical mission in a village.

247
00:15:21,520 --> 00:15:23,240
I enjoyed the French countryside

248
00:15:23,240 --> 00:15:24,800
and experienced local customs.

249
00:15:25,760 --> 00:15:28,440
What's the difference
between seeing patients

250
00:15:28,560 --> 00:15:29,560
in a village and a hospital?

251
00:15:30,080 --> 00:15:31,480
Look. You're tanned again.

252
00:15:31,840 --> 00:15:34,400
Listen, a young girl must do skin care.

253
00:15:34,560 --> 00:15:35,240
See?

254
00:15:35,960 --> 00:15:36,480
Sunscreen.

255
00:15:37,400 --> 00:15:38,960
It should be sprayed every two hours.

256
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:42,840
You know what? Don't be stingy on this.

257
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:44,400
Or you'll spend more
on whitening injections.

258
00:15:45,040 --> 00:15:46,640
OK. I get it.

259
00:15:46,640 --> 00:15:48,640
I don't go there every day.

260
00:15:48,840 --> 00:15:50,040
Nor am I exposed to the sun.

261
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:52,280
Then why are you tanned?

262
00:15:52,280 --> 00:15:53,040
Oh, no.

263
00:15:53,040 --> 00:15:54,320
You must have a metabolism problem

264
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:55,760
because you're getting aged.

265
00:15:55,960 --> 00:15:57,080
Metabolism?

266
00:15:57,760 --> 00:15:59,320
I'm not even 30.

267
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:01,480
What kind of mother talks like this?

268
00:16:01,640 --> 00:16:02,960
You're no match for me.

269
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:05,000
I have great genes.

270
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:08,080
When we go out together, people say

271
00:16:08,680 --> 00:16:09,480
we're sisters, huh?

272
00:16:10,840 --> 00:16:12,280
Who has such poor eyesight?

273
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:15,440
Come on. What's your point?

274
00:16:16,680 --> 00:16:17,680
Nothing.

275
00:16:18,240 --> 00:16:19,240
I just miss you.

276
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:22,160
Last week, when I gave treatments,

277
00:16:22,920 --> 00:16:24,160
I saw a little girl and her mother

278
00:16:24,560 --> 00:16:26,080
depending on each other to survive.

279
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:28,480
They reminded me of you.

280
00:16:30,040 --> 00:16:31,320
You had time to think of me?

281
00:16:31,920 --> 00:16:33,200
It means you're quite idle.

282
00:16:33,760 --> 00:16:35,160
You don't even have a boyfriend, huh?

283
00:16:38,240 --> 00:16:39,600
Why can you lead

284
00:16:39,880 --> 00:16:41,280
every conversation to this?

285
00:16:42,520 --> 00:16:43,680
Why didn't you ask

286
00:16:44,080 --> 00:16:45,240
if I was suffering out here?

287
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:49,440
You suffered because you asked for that.

288
00:16:49,680 --> 00:16:50,920
I didn't give you

289
00:16:51,040 --> 00:16:51,800
such a pretty face

290
00:16:51,800 --> 00:16:53,960
to face those lab instruments all day.

291
00:16:54,320 --> 00:16:55,160
What are you doing?

292
00:16:55,160 --> 00:16:56,960
Wasting your valuable time.

293
00:16:56,960 --> 00:16:57,960
Stop, stop.

294
00:16:59,240 --> 00:16:59,760
You win.

295
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:02,520
I'm an open-minded mother.

296
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:05,520
I just want you to have a relationship.

297
00:17:06,520 --> 00:17:08,200
A happy ending isn't that important.

298
00:17:08,400 --> 00:17:09,640
What matters is the process.

299
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:12,960
You won't keep waiting

300
00:17:12,960 --> 00:17:14,680
until you have a late-life love, huh?

301
00:17:17,760 --> 00:17:19,440
I think it's you who wants a boyfriend.

302
00:17:20,640 --> 00:17:21,800
Nonsense.

303
00:17:21,800 --> 00:17:22,440
Lan,

304
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:24,400
don't ever worry about that.

305
00:17:25,240 --> 00:17:26,160
I'm totally OK with it.

306
00:17:27,400 --> 00:17:29,000
Don't be kidding. I'll hang up.

307
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:30,040
I'll really be late.

308
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:42,080
Boss,

309
00:17:42,760 --> 00:17:44,400
our medical aid project will be over

310
00:17:44,400 --> 00:17:45,400
in two weeks.

311
00:17:45,520 --> 00:17:46,880
Fill the report sheets

312
00:17:46,880 --> 00:17:48,040
as soon as you can.

313
00:17:50,840 --> 00:17:52,040
The hospital official asked

314
00:17:52,040 --> 00:17:53,400
whether we would apply

315
00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:55,200
for medical aid for the following year

316
00:17:55,200 --> 00:17:56,560
or go back to China.

317
00:18:01,480 --> 00:18:02,320
Anything else?

318
00:18:03,720 --> 00:18:05,320
The Medical Department
asked me to remind you.

319
00:18:06,720 --> 00:18:08,160
Before you came to Lacaya,

320
00:18:08,160 --> 00:18:10,400
your glioma project was suspended.

321
00:18:11,320 --> 00:18:12,680
Since He Xiaoguang took it over,

322
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:14,040
no progress has been made.

323
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:15,880
If things go on like this,

324
00:18:16,120 --> 00:18:18,040
it can't get
the research fund for next year.

325
00:18:18,440 --> 00:18:19,960
And the Youth Talent Program.

326
00:18:20,200 --> 00:18:21,200
It's held every four years.

327
00:18:21,760 --> 00:18:23,440
If you don't return,

328
00:18:25,760 --> 00:18:27,400
He Xiaoguang is very likely to have it.

329
00:18:30,520 --> 00:18:33,000
So, are we or are we not going back?

330
00:18:38,320 --> 00:18:39,320
Boss,

331
00:18:40,600 --> 00:18:42,280
if we go back to China,

332
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:44,760
what about you and Su Wei'an?

333
00:18:47,360 --> 00:18:48,360
Are you

334
00:18:48,360 --> 00:18:49,400
in a relationship now?

335
00:18:51,240 --> 00:18:52,920
If you return to China,

336
00:18:52,920 --> 00:18:54,040
will she go with you?

337
00:18:58,520 --> 00:18:59,880
Did Jiang Muying send you?

338
00:19:02,360 --> 00:19:04,240
I... I just think

339
00:19:04,240 --> 00:19:06,560
it's hard for you to keep pretending

340
00:19:08,840 --> 00:19:10,120
your foot hasn't recovered.

341
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:10,920
Right?

342
00:19:13,760 --> 00:19:14,800
Hasn't recovered?

343
00:19:16,800 --> 00:19:17,880
Watch this, then.

344
00:19:18,800 --> 00:19:20,160
Just kidding.

345
00:19:26,160 --> 00:19:28,240
Your foot hasn't recovered. Do not move.

346
00:19:28,440 --> 00:19:29,240
I'm OK.

347
00:19:31,920 --> 00:19:32,640
Does it still hurt?

348
00:19:33,960 --> 00:19:35,280
Yes. It hurts a lot.

349
00:19:36,760 --> 00:19:37,760
Wait.

350
00:19:38,720 --> 00:19:39,920
These days,

351
00:19:40,440 --> 00:19:41,600
you could even perform surgery.

352
00:19:42,320 --> 00:19:43,560
Why is it still so serious?

353
00:19:45,280 --> 00:19:46,880
I can sit during the surgery.

354
00:19:47,240 --> 00:19:50,080
So, a foot injury doesn't interfere.

355
00:19:54,320 --> 00:19:55,320
What are you laughing at?

356
00:19:58,080 --> 00:19:59,160
Fang Mingfan,

357
00:19:59,160 --> 00:20:00,680
don't you have an emergency treatment?

358
00:20:02,040 --> 00:20:02,960
What emergency...?

359
00:20:07,040 --> 00:20:07,920
Oh, yes.

360
00:20:08,240 --> 00:20:09,240
I have one.

361
00:20:10,400 --> 00:20:11,840
I'll leave Boss to you.

362
00:20:17,660 --> 00:20:19,400
[Gu Yunzheng]

363
00:20:19,400 --> 00:20:20,720
You can give surgery.

364
00:20:20,720 --> 00:20:21,920
So, you don't have a big problem.

365
00:20:22,240 --> 00:20:23,360
Rest for recuperation.

366
00:20:23,520 --> 00:20:24,440
Wait.

367
00:20:30,840 --> 00:20:32,920
Want to leave after taking my gown?

368
00:20:33,680 --> 00:20:35,360
The lounge is too cold. So, I...

369
00:20:36,080 --> 00:20:36,840
I took it casually.

370
00:20:37,400 --> 00:20:38,440
Casually?

371
00:20:40,520 --> 00:20:42,920
I had an injured foot because of you.

372
00:20:43,120 --> 00:20:44,880
Are you going to leave me alone?

373
00:20:45,600 --> 00:20:46,640
What do you want?

374
00:20:49,640 --> 00:20:52,080
You must have learned this in college.

375
00:20:52,560 --> 00:20:54,240
In human saliva,

376
00:20:54,240 --> 00:20:56,520
there's something called opiorphin.

377
00:20:57,080 --> 00:20:58,240
Its analgesic effect

378
00:20:58,240 --> 00:21:00,240
is as good as morphine.

379
00:21:00,360 --> 00:21:01,160
So,

380
00:21:02,440 --> 00:21:05,240
a kiss helps to ease the pain.

381
00:21:27,200 --> 00:21:28,400
I never expected to see this.

382
00:21:28,760 --> 00:21:30,520
My cool boss

383
00:21:30,960 --> 00:21:32,160
was even rejected.

384
00:21:34,320 --> 00:21:35,560
Do you have too much free time?

385
00:21:36,240 --> 00:21:38,440
Do you want emergency calls for a week?

386
00:21:40,040 --> 00:21:40,600
I'm sorry.

387
00:21:42,120 --> 00:21:44,760
♪Be frank in love♪

388
00:21:44,760 --> 00:21:46,640
Don't sing so loudly in the hospital.

389
00:21:46,640 --> 00:21:47,520
Shut up!

390
00:21:50,700 --> 00:21:53,260
[Jinhai City]

391
00:22:05,940 --> 00:22:07,900
[Wen Ran]

392
00:22:07,920 --> 00:22:08,640
Yuncheng,

393
00:22:08,640 --> 00:22:11,160
my father invited you over
for dinner this weekend.

394
00:22:11,360 --> 00:22:12,400
What would you like to eat?

395
00:22:12,720 --> 00:22:14,160
I'll get the ingredients ready.

396
00:22:14,880 --> 00:22:16,760
Or shall we
go grocery shopping together?

397
00:22:17,200 --> 00:22:18,840
I love to go grocery shopping with you.

398
00:22:19,780 --> 00:22:24,420
[I'm not going this weekend.
I'll be on a business trip abroad.]

399
00:22:27,760 --> 00:22:28,360
Come on in.

400
00:22:28,680 --> 00:22:29,160
Mr. Du.

401
00:22:30,240 --> 00:22:32,240
Have you booked
my flight ticket to Lacaya?

402
00:22:32,240 --> 00:22:32,840
Yes.

403
00:22:32,840 --> 00:22:34,800
But I have something to tell you.

404
00:22:35,680 --> 00:22:36,200
Go ahead.

405
00:22:36,400 --> 00:22:38,400
The clinical trial of Phase III of HDQ39

406
00:22:38,400 --> 00:22:39,400
has started.

407
00:22:39,680 --> 00:22:41,240
To pump up the stock price,

408
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:43,240
the board wants
to hold a news conference,

409
00:22:43,400 --> 00:22:45,040
and they hope
you can attend it in person.

410
00:22:46,720 --> 00:22:47,960
Then hold it after I'm back.

411
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:50,160
The recruitment
will officially start next Monday.

412
00:22:50,160 --> 00:22:52,160
Will it be too late when you...?

413
00:22:54,640 --> 00:22:55,360
Give it to me.

414
00:22:56,760 --> 00:22:58,520
How much you commit to this project

415
00:22:58,520 --> 00:23:00,400
determines the attitude of the board.

416
00:23:00,800 --> 00:23:02,760
If you attend the conference in person,

417
00:23:03,040 --> 00:23:05,800
the future fund application
will go more smoothly.

418
00:23:11,280 --> 00:23:14,040
Well, you cancel my flight ticket.

419
00:23:14,240 --> 00:23:14,760
OK.

420
00:23:24,380 --> 00:23:26,980
[Friendship Hospital]
[Lacaya]

421
00:23:37,480 --> 00:23:39,000
[Fang Mingfan]
(But for Su Wei'an,)

422
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:40,240
(he'll change his mind, I think.)

423
00:23:40,360 --> 00:23:41,160
(He's hesitating.)

424
00:23:41,560 --> 00:23:43,440
(I'll get more information for you.)

425
00:23:47,180 --> 00:23:48,180
[Gu Yunzheng]

426
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:54,040
Don't stare at me.

427
00:24:01,760 --> 00:24:02,400
Jiang.

428
00:24:04,240 --> 00:24:05,880
Do you have

429
00:24:06,280 --> 00:24:07,760
skin-lightening products?

430
00:24:09,760 --> 00:24:11,240
Why do you suddenly want that?

431
00:24:11,360 --> 00:24:12,920
Didn't you scorn me

432
00:24:12,920 --> 00:24:13,960
for doing skincare all day?

433
00:24:16,040 --> 00:24:17,960
A girl dolls herself up
for him who loves her.

434
00:24:18,360 --> 00:24:18,920
Su Wei'an.

435
00:24:22,240 --> 00:24:23,320
What did you

436
00:24:23,600 --> 00:24:24,400
and Gu Yunzheng do

437
00:24:25,120 --> 00:24:26,640
in the wild over two days and one night?

438
00:24:28,680 --> 00:24:29,640
Nothing.

439
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:32,560
That was a perfect chance.

440
00:24:32,560 --> 00:24:34,120
But you didn't get Gu Yunzheng.

441
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:37,120
You turned a love night
into a wild adventure.

442
00:24:37,560 --> 00:24:38,640
You just wasted the rainstorm

443
00:24:38,640 --> 00:24:40,200
God arranged for you.

444
00:24:41,080 --> 00:24:43,240
Hey, what are you thinking every day?

445
00:24:44,080 --> 00:24:45,720
Why must we do something?

446
00:24:47,080 --> 00:24:49,680
I feel anxious for you, Wei'an.

447
00:24:50,080 --> 00:24:52,400
If you don't hurry up,
he'll go back to China.

448
00:24:54,240 --> 00:24:54,920
Go back to China?

449
00:24:56,040 --> 00:24:56,400
Why?

450
00:24:56,840 --> 00:24:57,720
Fang Mingfan said

451
00:24:58,040 --> 00:25:00,120
their medical aid project
would be over soon,

452
00:25:00,120 --> 00:25:00,840
and they would return.

453
00:25:01,160 --> 00:25:02,160
Gu Yunzheng didn't tell you?

454
00:25:07,280 --> 00:25:08,360
I understand.

455
00:25:08,800 --> 00:25:09,760
After all,

456
00:25:11,040 --> 00:25:12,480
you wasted that perfect chance

457
00:25:12,480 --> 00:25:13,560
in Labe Village.

458
00:25:13,560 --> 00:25:14,320
I guess

459
00:25:14,320 --> 00:25:16,080
he thinks you have no feelings for him,

460
00:25:17,160 --> 00:25:20,200
so he doesn't dare
to invite you back to China.

461
00:25:24,400 --> 00:25:26,040
I really don't understand you.

462
00:25:26,640 --> 00:25:28,960
He's such a great handsome man.

463
00:25:29,160 --> 00:25:30,840
And you got a big crush on him.

464
00:25:31,320 --> 00:25:32,360
He's right in front of you,

465
00:25:32,360 --> 00:25:33,800
and you'll let him leave like that.

466
00:25:34,360 --> 00:25:35,560
This is my ideal of life.

467
00:25:36,160 --> 00:25:37,920
Even if Mars crashed into Earth tomorrow

468
00:25:37,920 --> 00:25:38,960
and destroyed the world,

469
00:25:39,600 --> 00:25:41,800
I would enjoy a remarkable love.

470
00:25:42,520 --> 00:25:43,960
Or my life would be wasted.

471
00:25:53,360 --> 00:25:55,360
He's going back to China,
but he said that to me.

472
00:25:57,960 --> 00:25:59,360
What did he mean?

473
00:26:09,560 --> 00:26:11,120
What? Have you decided?

474
00:26:11,120 --> 00:26:12,000
Where are we going?

475
00:26:13,080 --> 00:26:14,160
Keep driving.

476
00:26:16,280 --> 00:26:17,720
You can't be kidnapping me, huh?

477
00:26:20,920 --> 00:26:23,440
Have you seen a kidnapper
sit in the front passenger seat

478
00:26:23,440 --> 00:26:24,880
while the hostage drives?

479
00:26:28,320 --> 00:26:29,680
You have a foot injury.

480
00:26:29,760 --> 00:26:31,760
Instead of staying in the hospital,
you came out.

481
00:26:31,960 --> 00:26:33,480
And you made me drive.

482
00:26:34,360 --> 00:26:36,240
But you asked me to charter your car.

483
00:26:36,760 --> 00:26:37,960
Don't you want to make money?

484
00:26:38,760 --> 00:26:39,560
I do.

485
00:26:42,600 --> 00:26:43,960
So, where are we going?

486
00:26:46,600 --> 00:26:48,600
I learned about a local tribe

487
00:26:48,760 --> 00:26:51,080
where there's a very famous witch doctor

488
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:53,800
who takes care of incurable diseases.

489
00:26:54,120 --> 00:26:56,440
I'll have him handle my foot injury.

490
00:26:59,200 --> 00:26:59,640
Come on.

491
00:26:59,640 --> 00:27:01,480
You're an associate professor at Huaren.

492
00:27:02,920 --> 00:27:04,840
Show a little respect for science, OK?

493
00:27:05,200 --> 00:27:07,200
In terms of modern medicine,

494
00:27:07,200 --> 00:27:09,120
my foot injury should have recovered.

495
00:27:09,400 --> 00:27:11,160
But now, it still hasn't.

496
00:27:11,760 --> 00:27:16,120
I think some evil energy
must have invaded my body.

497
00:27:16,200 --> 00:27:17,200
It's already something

498
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:19,400
that modern medicine can't explain.

499
00:27:19,800 --> 00:27:21,520
I have to try something else.

500
00:27:23,640 --> 00:27:25,360
Turn right at the end of the road.

501
00:27:26,800 --> 00:27:29,040
Just so you know, you should pay double.

502
00:27:32,600 --> 00:27:33,960
OK. No problem.

503
00:27:48,560 --> 00:27:50,160
Is this where the witch doctor lives?

504
00:27:54,840 --> 00:27:55,840
Quite special.

505
00:27:56,960 --> 00:27:58,320
Is he out for work?

506
00:28:02,240 --> 00:28:03,040
Look.

507
00:28:03,960 --> 00:28:05,000
The navigation led us here.

508
00:28:07,480 --> 00:28:08,280
OK.

509
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:10,040
I'll also get a witch doctor

510
00:28:10,400 --> 00:28:11,440
and open a branch here.

511
00:28:11,440 --> 00:28:13,080
If someone has no cure
in Friendship Hospital,

512
00:28:13,080 --> 00:28:14,960
Dr. Gu, please take him here.

513
00:28:15,040 --> 00:28:16,360
I'll make a big fortune.

514
00:28:19,240 --> 00:28:20,200
Maybe

515
00:28:20,400 --> 00:28:21,800
this tree gets a soul.

516
00:28:22,840 --> 00:28:23,640
You know what?

517
00:28:24,440 --> 00:28:25,240
My foot

518
00:28:27,080 --> 00:28:29,280
doesn't feel as painful as before. Look.

519
00:28:41,320 --> 00:28:42,120
Go.

520
00:28:42,760 --> 00:28:43,880
Let me take you somewhere.

521
00:28:50,760 --> 00:28:51,560
Look.

522
00:28:57,040 --> 00:28:58,200
This is marvelous.

523
00:29:01,400 --> 00:29:04,000
This bridge was built by Chinese people.

524
00:29:04,640 --> 00:29:06,160
I've been in Lacaya for over a year

525
00:29:06,840 --> 00:29:08,640
and crossed many bridges
built by Chinese people.

526
00:29:10,040 --> 00:29:11,080
I keep wondering

527
00:29:12,880 --> 00:29:13,840
if one of these bridges

528
00:29:13,840 --> 00:29:15,400
was built by my mother.

529
00:29:20,640 --> 00:29:21,680
Some must be.

530
00:29:22,840 --> 00:29:26,040
Your mother is an honorable lady.

531
00:29:31,960 --> 00:29:32,640
Yeah.

532
00:29:33,480 --> 00:29:34,760
If she weren't my mother,

533
00:29:35,440 --> 00:29:36,240
maybe

534
00:29:37,480 --> 00:29:38,920
I would like her.

535
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:49,320
Let's say hi to it.

536
00:29:52,920 --> 00:29:53,720
Hi!

537
00:30:00,800 --> 00:30:02,000
Hi!

538
00:30:02,000 --> 00:30:03,280
How are you doing?

539
00:30:17,440 --> 00:30:19,440
Can it be Nero Bridge?

540
00:30:21,880 --> 00:30:24,400
I hear there's a day
for Light Festival every year.

541
00:30:25,160 --> 00:30:27,000
I've stayed in Lacaya for a long time,

542
00:30:27,200 --> 00:30:28,440
but I just haven't witnessed it.

543
00:30:29,720 --> 00:30:30,520
Yeah.

544
00:30:31,680 --> 00:30:34,440
You must have been busy making money.

545
00:30:40,160 --> 00:30:41,880
You ran quite fast.

546
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:44,200
Your foot doesn't hurt, huh?

547
00:30:44,800 --> 00:30:47,120
It does. It still hurts.

548
00:31:11,200 --> 00:31:12,000
Want a try?

549
00:31:27,880 --> 00:31:28,880
Are you OK?

550
00:31:29,800 --> 00:31:30,680
Are you fine?

551
00:31:31,480 --> 00:31:32,520
You know what?

552
00:31:33,240 --> 00:31:36,000
Racing makes your brain release dopamine

553
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:37,320
and get excited.

554
00:31:37,880 --> 00:31:39,320
So does love.

555
00:31:40,240 --> 00:31:42,280
Looks like I work better
than that witch doctor.

556
00:31:42,440 --> 00:31:44,000
Your foot has almost recovered, huh?

557
00:31:44,960 --> 00:31:45,640
Pay me.

558
00:31:47,000 --> 00:31:47,840
What?

559
00:31:48,160 --> 00:31:50,760
The hostage
asked the kidnapper for money?

560
00:31:50,880 --> 00:31:52,360
You look more like a hostage.

561
00:31:54,760 --> 00:31:55,840
I have no money.

562
00:31:56,240 --> 00:31:58,000
If you want me, you can get it.

563
00:31:59,480 --> 00:32:00,240
What did you say?

564
00:32:00,240 --> 00:32:01,240
I can't hear you.

565
00:32:02,000 --> 00:32:03,840
We're stopping here. Don't pretend.

566
00:32:05,080 --> 00:32:05,960
You can't hear me?

567
00:32:06,280 --> 00:32:07,080
Guess.

